comment:
21.05.2016 тhe guards of the actor Jerry Judge and Sean Belt said that they were in the hallway of the star couple's house when they heard Amber Heard screaming: "Stop hitting me." Just a second later, they were at the scene and saw Johnny Depp in the kitchen, and his wife on the couch in the living room. There were at least seven meters between them.
The bodyguards also emphasize that during the fifteen months of marriage, it was Heard who most often initiated conflicts, it was she who threw various objects, including bottles, at her husband in anger, and sometimes they had to drag her away from Depp by force.
The owners of their house on Broadway claimed that Amber had no signs of violence, two days after the incident, and they even complimented her that she looked good. She was not wearing makeup and there were no signs of violence. The lawyer, who lives in this building, said that two concierge said there were no signs of violence. One saw her on May 23, 2016, the other on May 25, 2016.
Moreover, on May 22, 2016, Amber was at a party with her friend Amanda de Cadenet, smiling and taking pictures with the guests:
Needless to say, this photo, posted by one of the guests in insta, was deleted the next day.
author: Зоя Бельская
